    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles to start and requires significant mechanical attention, while the body shows heavy rust and multiple dents from previous incidents. The interior also has considerable wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics, so please expect to invest time and money into repairs.",
