    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative vehicle, maintained in truly immaculate condition. This is an exemplary specimen, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original factory luster. Every detail has been meticulously curated to ensure it meets the rigorous standards of a premier automotive investment. For the discerning individual who accepts no compromises in quality or performance, this vehicle offers an unparalleled driving experience. Fully inspected and prepared for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or a speck of dust anywhere! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a total gem that\u2019s been kept in perfect shape, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a pristine E46 M3 that serves as a benchmark for the S54 platform. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance cycle, including Beisan Systems VANOS seals and WPC-treated rod bearings. The chassis is structurally sound, featuring a proactive subframe reinforcement with epoxy-injected plates to ensure torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission with a refreshed shift linkage for bolt-action precision. The suspension geometry remains stock but has been enhanced with Powerflex bushings to eliminate deflection. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero thermal cycling fatigue on the plastics and a flawless undercarriage free of oxidation.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Clean title. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem: a 2021 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and remains in pristine showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with blue contrast stitching looks and smells brand new; the seat bolsters show no signs of entry wear, and the original factory protective film remains on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, having strictly followed a dealership break-in service schedule and subsequent annual maintenance despite the low mileage. With only 4,200 miles on the odometer, this is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic in its purest form. The car features a perfect set of 788M forged wheels with deep tread on the original Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires. It includes both original keys, all owner manuals, a custom-fit car cover, and a comprehensive service history. Non-smoker, no pets, and never once driven in inclement weather.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This unit exhibits no discernible wear and possesses a flawless service history, representing a rare acquisition opportunity for the discerning enthusiast. Every aspect of this motorcar has been preserved to the highest standards, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the uncompromising quality of this pristine asset.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's in incredible shape\u2014no scratches, no spills, and it drives like a total dream! I've taken such good care of it, and I'm looking for a new owner who will love it just as much. It's been kept in a climate-controlled garage and has a full service history. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
